\newlabel{tab:handcalc}{{1.4}{11}{Analytical hand-calculation agreement. The launch discrepancy is expected: the simulation's \SI {80}{\milli \second } torque ramp (Section~\ref {sec:launch}) actively suppresses peak torque below the unramped analytical value}{table.caption.8}{}}
